beer.beer_description:
Hops.  More Hops.  And then some more Hops for good measure.  So hoppy, our brewers got kicked out of bed by their wives and had to sleep on the couch because they were sweating hops.
we start with a massively hopped West Coast Double IPA, then load it with generous dosing's of our own house made steam distilled Nelson Sauvin Hop Oil.
  
Boasting a huge tropical and pine hop punch to the face followed by an intense bitter kick to the tongue to balance the malt and alcohol sweetness, with a dank, resinous finish from the Hop Oil.
